---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
import Hero from '@components/Hero.astro'
import Feature from '@components/Feature.astro'
import Counter from '@components/Counter.astro'
import ContentMedia from '@components/ContentMedia.astro'
import LinkComponent from '@components/LinkComponent.astro'
import { Accordion, AccordionItem, Avatar, AvatarGroup } from 'accessible-astro-components'
---

<DefaultLayout title="Home">
  <Hero />

  <section class="my-32 md:my-64">
    <div class="space-content container">
      <h2 class="font-6">A New Standard for Decentralized Finance</h2>
      <div class="text-2xl">
        <p>
          Welcome to TitanX, a hyper-deflationary DeFi 3.0 ecosystem built from the ground up with no insiders, no
          pre-sales, and no compromises. 100% fair launch. 100% community-owned. Designed for long-term value.
        </p>
        <p>
          TitanX was born from a simple belief: DeFi should belong to the many, not the few. No venture capital. No
          privileged insiders. Just code, community, and unstoppable innovation. Build On TitanX (#BoT) is a new concept
          lived out on this page by ensuring that every particpant can find the knowledge they need.
        </p>
        <p>
          We’re creating the world’s first hyper-deflationary, fully fair-launched DeFi ecosystem — one that empowers
          builders, rewards users, and restores trust in decentralized finance. If you believe in transparency,
          composability, and merit-based value — you’re in the right place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-32 md:my-64">
    <ContentMedia imgSrc="/TitanX-Stats_06-08-2025.webp">
      <h2>TitanX is the grassroots, pure crypto movement</h2>
      <p class="text-2xl">
        no insiders, no VC control, no inflation. Fair-launched on Ethereum, fully transparent, and built where the
        users and builders already are. Checkout: <LinkComponent href="https://app.titanx.win/stats"
          >TitanX Stats</LinkComponent
        >
      </p>
    </ContentMedia>

    <ContentMedia imgSrc="/ETHBASE_Logos.webp" reverseImg={true}>
      <h2>Build, invest, and earn in a deflationary DeFi ecosystem</h2>
      <p class="text-2xl">
        that rewards real usage, not hype. TitanX leverages proven L1 and L2 networks for instant compatibility with the
        tools you already use. The main Focus is on Ethereum and BASE for now.
        <!-- But  Pulsechain also finds more and more support. -->
      </p>
    </ContentMedia>
  </section>

  <section class="my-32 md:my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">Why TitanX</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <Feature icon="lucide:banknote" title="Hyper-Deflationary by Design">
          No inflation, no emissions, no supply creep. Every action that drives value also strengthens scarcity —
          rewarding long-term participants.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:blocks" title="Built by Builders, for Builders">
          No teams hoarding tokens. No insiders waiting to dump. You build it, you earn. Value is created by
          contributions, not connections.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:handshake" title="100% Fair Launch">
          No presales, no allocations, no VC wallets. Everyone started at the same line — the only way to earn is to
          contribute.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:shield-check" title="Triple-Audited & Secure">
          TitanX code has undergone multiple third-party audits, making it one of the most rigorously tested DeFi
          projects on-chain.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:puzzle" title="Composable Across Chains">
          TitanX doesn’t compete with L1s — it amplifies them. By maximizing composability and integrating where users
          already are, we enable seamless adoption.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:users" title="Fully Community-Driven">
          The Community and most of all the Builders are in the center of attention. Meritocracy is key and efforts are rewarded.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:flame" title="Proof of Burn 2.0">
          Every protocol built in the ecosystem burns and/or locks $TITANX and makes it more rare.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:layers" title="Vertically Stacked LPs">
          Every protocol benefits from the adoption of another protocol by linking all LPs together.
        </Feature>
        <Feature icon="lucide:goal" title="One core goal">
          Create hyper deflationary, community-owned, DeFi 3.0 assets. Supporting eachother.
        </Feature>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-32 md:my-64">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-6xl">FAQ</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl">
          TitanX Is DeFi, as It Should Be — No shortcuts. No special treatment. Just a fair, secure, and scalable
          ecosystem designed to unlock true decentralization — and reward those who help build it.
        </p>
        <LinkComponent class="button color-secondary" href="https://www.titanxhub.com/">Ecosystem</LinkComponent>
        <LinkComponent class="button" href="https://www.titanxinfo.com/">More Information</LinkComponent>
      </div>
      <div class="space-content">
        <Accordion class="accordionReset">
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="What is TITANX, and why is it so unique?" open>
            <p>
              TITANX is a grassroots crypto ecosystem built around fairness, decentralization, and builder-first
              principles. No VCs, no premines—just open infrastructure, fair launches, and code-driven alignment between
              users and developers.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Why is $TITANX 'Hyper Deflationary'?">
            <p>
              $TITANX supply decreases over time via on-chain burn mechanics. Usage triggers burns, making the token
              scarcer as adoption grows. There's no inflation or emissions schedule—only deflation tied to ecosystem
              activity.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Why are so many builders attracted to building on $TITANX?">
            <p>
              TITANX gives builders full autonomy. No gatekeepers, no closed ecosystems. Smart contracts, tools, and
              rewards are open to all. Builders earn visibility and value by shipping real products—not by marketing or
              insider deals.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Where do I buy $TITANX?">
            <p>
              $TITANX is traded on decentralized exchanges. Use official sources to verify token contracts. Availability
              depends on the chain—no centralized listing, no custody risk, fully on-chain.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Why is the focus on fair launches so pronounced here?">
            <p>
              Fair launches prevent early insider advantage and align incentives with actual contributors. TITANX
              projects launch publicly, transparently, and without private allocations. Builders earn trust by
              delivering—not by pre-sale hype.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
          <AccordionItem name="exclusive" title="Where can I get more educated on $TITANX & its ecosystem?">
            <p>
              Start at <a href="https://titanx.win" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">titanx.win</a>. Read the
              docs, explore builder tools, and follow on-chain deployments. Education is open, public, and driven by
              contributors—not centralized marketing.
            </p>
          </AccordionItem>
        </Accordion>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

